- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper uses natural language processing techniques to analyze the sentiment of tweets. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper may touch upon issues related to cybersecurity and privacy in the context of social media data analysis.
